I have added payment method but I am still getting warning on ads saying i need to add payment method

It sounds like there might be an issue with the payment method you've added. Please make sure that your payment method is valid and correctly associated with your account. If you're using ad credits, ensure you also have a primary payment method on file. If the problem persists, I recommend contacting your bank or adding a different payment method. You can also try resubmitting your ads after updating the payment details. For more detailed guidance, you can check out our Billing Guide here: [Billing Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17821681919757-Billing-Guide).
